, 10VIII2013 (17:00), beaten from 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Quercus rubra" order="Fagales" pageId="4" pageNumber="99" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubra">Quercus rubra</taxonomicName>
, P. de Tonnancour (1, CPTO); same except: 8VIII2015 (15:00), beaten from 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Alnus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Alnus rugosa" order="Fagales" pageId="4" pageNumber="99" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rugosa">Alnus rugosa</taxonomicName>
(1, CPTO), beaten from 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Betula" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Betula populifolia" order="Fagales" pageId="4" pageNumber="99" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="populifolia">Betula populifolia</taxonomicName>
(2, CPTO) or swept from various herbaceous plants in gray birch stand (1, CPTO); same except: 10VIII2015 (13:00), swept from various herbaceous plants in gray birch stand (2, CPTO); same except: 16VIII2015 (15:00), beaten from 
